      "schemeDefinitions": [],
      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a permanent resident of Odisha.  \n1. The applicant should possess identity and residential proof including an Aadhar card.\n1. The applicant should have a bank account in his/her name in the State of Odisha.\n1. The applicant should have requisite land free from all encumbrances. \n1. The pond area must be between 0.2 to 2.00 hectares with a minimum water depth of 6 feet.\n1. Previous beneficiaries of similar subsidies are eligible for additional subsidies up to a total of 2 hectares.\n\n",
